    "DreamSync [157] and StyleAdapter [158] use LoRA to improve text fidelity and image quality.",
    "Mix-of-Show [159] captures out-of-domain information with LoRA weights to combine multiple customized concepts with high fidelity, reducing concept conflicts.",
